commit ad00e5bad1f19ed24417170a6a17dee8addff69f
Author: Meekness Adesina <zenon8adams@gmail.com>
Date:   Sun Nov 19 23:17:26 2023 +0100

    Source/Fix: Resolve sticky cursor on drag
    
    If window is in drag mode and the cursor gets captured
    by a button, vfunc_key_release_event will not be
    triggered. The old implementation depends on this
    event to be fired before releasing the cursor. To fix
    this, we listen to enter-event on all buttons and
    release the cursor on receiving such event.
    
    Window tiling mode is disabled due to implementation
    flaw. If would certainly be fixed in the next release.
    
    Signed-off-by: Meekness Adesina <zenon8adams@gmail.com>

