commit ed503c953ea0330c1dad2497f68789943c15d99c
Author: Meekness Adesina <zenon8adams@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Nov 2 23:29:17 2023 +0100

    Source/Minor: Build separate thumbnail view
    
    The UI has been redesigned with a new idea of
    thumbnails. Each shots taken are stored
    in the `USER_CACHE_DIR` which resolves
    to ~/.cache on debian. These are loaded into
    a viewport which displays a tiny thumbnail.
    Any of the entries in the side view when
    clicked, expands into a bigger view pane.
    
    Upcoming:
        - Implement a smarter expansion mechanism
          for the side view. Currently, the
          view expands in an horrible manner.
        - Improve hacks in code.
    
    Signed-off-by: Meekness Adesina <zenon8adams@gmail.com>

